data.description: Pride in ownership! Stunning open floorplan.  3 bdrm + Den. 2.5 bth. Walk in closets in all rooms. Jack n Jill for bdrm 2 & 3. Seamless laundry access to primary closet 1 and Primary bath suite. Primary suite his n her sinks and closets.  Stylish features include 23 x 11 tile throughout. Shutters and window screens. Crown moldings. Shiplap family room wall. Open kitchen boasts an island, pantry, gas stove top, butler xtra area. Enjoy eat in kitchen area. Foam insulation including attic. Privacy with no behind neighbors and a scenic desert back. Extended patio open to beautiful artificial grass, pavers, and BBQ for entertaining. Spa does convey.
